      "content": "ok i get that i might be a bit groggy the next day, but i'm mostly worried about the sleep part. if the alcohol makes the sedation stronger, doesn't that just mean it's more effective at knocking me out? i just want to make sure i'm not doing something crazy. if it's just one small glass, is it actually dangerous or is it just a bit more relaxing?",
